      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CHERYL BLUE (5) is a talented dog who is a winner of nine races but missed the frame last time when sixth at The Meadows (30.68). Form here at the trip excellent including three wins. The form out of last race has been strong. Looks the one to beat on her best form. BEAR MAN (2) has been hard to follow lately, running fourth (20.38) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. Rates a winning chance on best. BRONTE BEACH (1) was rewarded for his honesty after two minors on end with a deserved win last time, scoring at Dubbo over 318m (18.61). Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Can make it two on the bounce. SUNNY BLUE (4) was in the money last start at this track and distance - poses a threat again.",
